@copilot we don't needs backwards compat as this control does not even exist yet. 

@copilot can we also do the velocity and pressure together thing like windows has.

This setting is valid for pencil and ballpoint pen brushes.

For the ballpoint pen brush, a faster velocity results in a thinner stroke, while a lower velocity results in a thicker stroke.

We should also store this velocity in the path as some apps may want to lighten the colors on the faster strokes. Can you investigate if we can do this. So the faster you write the lighter and thinner it gets.
